org.apache.hadoop.hdds.scm.client

Class HddsClientUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hdds.scm.client.HddsClientUtils

  • @InterfaceAudience.Public
 @InterfaceStability.Unstable
public final class HddsClientUtils
extends Object
    Utility methods for Ozone and Container Clients. The methods to retrieve SCM service endpoints assume there is a single SCM service instance. This will change when we switch to replicated service instances for redundancy.
